overnment%20over%20the%20killing%20of%20former%20Lok%20Sabha%20member%20Atiq%20Ahmed%20and%20his%20brother%20Ashraf%20in%20police%20custody%20in%20Prayagraj%20on%20April%2015%2C%20observing%20%26quot%3Bsomeone%20is%20complicit%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20sought%20a%20status%20report%20from%20the%20state%20government%20on%20183%20%26quot%3Bpolice%20encounters%26quot%3B%20that%20have%20taken%20place%20since%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20state%20police%2C%20183%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20numerous%20police%20encounters%20since%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20government%20assumed%20office%20in%20March%202017.%20The%20chief%20minister's%20detractors%20have%20often%20claimed%20many%20of%20them%20were%20staged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20S%20Ravindra%20Bhat%20and%20Aravind%20Kumar%20directed%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20on%20Friday%20to%20file%20an%20affidavit%20within%20six%20weeks%20giving%20the%20details%20of%20these%20encounters%2C%20the%20status%20of%20investigation%2C%20charge%20sheets%20filed%20and%20the%20status%20of%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%205%20to%2010%20people%20guarding%20him%20(Atiq)...How%20can%20someone%20just%20come%20and%20shoot%3F%20How%20does%20this%20happen%3F%20Someone%20is%20complicit%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20issued%20notice%20to%20the%20UP%20government%20on%20a%20plea%20by%20Aisha%20Noori%2C%20sister%20of%20gangster-politician%20Ahmed%2C%20seeking%20a%20direction%20for%20a%20comprehensive%20probe%20into%20the%20killing%20of%20her%20brothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20however%2C%20rejected%20the%20request%20of%20PIL%20petitioner%20Vishal%20Tiwari%20for%20institution%20of%20an%20independent%20judicial%20commission%20of%20inquiry%20to%20go%20into%20the%20police%20encounters%20and%20the%20role%20of%20the%20men%20in%20uniform%20in%20these%2C%20saying%20the%20state%20government%20has%20already%20formed%20such%20a%20commission.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20earlier%20agreed%20to%20hear%20the%20pleas%2C%20including%20the%20one%20filed%20by%20Aisha%20Noori%2C%20seeking%20the%20constitution%20of%20a%20commission%20of%20inquiry%20chaired%20by%20a%20retired%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20into%20the%20%26quot%3Bextra-judicial%26quot%3B%20killing%20of%20her%20brothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhmed%20(60)%20and%20Ashraf%20were%20shot%20dead%20at%20point-blank%20range%20by%20three%20men%20posing%20as%20journalists%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20media%20interaction%20while%20police%20personnel%20were%20escorting%20them%20to%20a%20medical%20college%20for%20examination%20on%20April%2015.%20The%20entire%20shooting%20was%20captured%20live%20on%20national%20television.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20affidavit%20filed%20in%20the%20top%20court%2C%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20said%20the%20state%20is%20%26quot%3Bleaving%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20ensuring%20a%20thorough%2C%20impartial%20and%20timely%20investigation%26quot%3B%20into%20the%20deaths%20of%20Ahmed%20and%20Ashraf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20status%20report%20contained%20in%20the%20affidavit%20deals%20with%20inquiry%20into%20the%20April%2015%20incident%2C%20steps%20taken%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20deaths%20of%20Mohd%20Asad%20Khan%2C%20son%20of%20Ahmed%2C%20and%20Mohd%20Ghulam%20on%20April%2013%2C%20and%20also%20the%20measures%20initiated%20to%20implement%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20Justice%20B%20S%20Chauhan%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20Justice%20Chauhan%20headed%20the%20commission%20that%20probed%20the%20encounter%20killing%20of%20gangster%20Vikas%20Dubey%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDubey%20and%20his%20men%20had%20ambushed%20and%20killed%20eight%20policemen%20at%20his%20native%20Bikru%20village%20in%20Kanpur%20district%20in%20July%202020.%20He%20was%20arrested%20in%20Ujjain%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20was%20being%20brought%20back%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20police's%20custody%20when%20he%20allegedly%20tried%20to%20escape%20and%20was%20shot%20dead.%20Doubts%20were%20raised%20about%20the%20genuineness%20of%20the%20police%20encounter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20status%20report%20gave%20the%20details%20about%20the%20steps%20taken%20to%20implement%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20Justice%20Chauhan%20commission%2C%20which%20had%20concluded%20that%20the%20police%20version%20of%20the%20deaths%20of%20Dubey%20and%20his%20associates%20in%20retaliatory%20firing%20incidents%20in%20the%20days%20following%20his%20encounter%20killing%20could%20not%20be%20doubted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20there%20has%20been%20an%20overhaul%20of%20manpower%20reform%20and%20a%20total%20of%2010%2C877%20posts%20at%20various%20levels%20have%20been%20created%20in%20the%20police%20department%20from%20April%2011%2C%202021%20till%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFurther%2C%20action%20on%20requisitioning%20of%201%2C12%2C177%20posts%20of%20various%20cadres%20is%20also%20under%20progress%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20status%20report%20said%20the%20police%20department%20has%20also%20undergone%20a%20modernisation%2C%20following%20purchase%20of%20prison%20vans%2C%20drones%2C%20postmortem%20kits%20and%20various%20other%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20number%20of%20forensic%20science%20laboratories%20(FSLs)%20has%20increased%20from%20eight%20to%2012%20with%20new%20facilities%20having%20been%20established%20in%20Kannauj%2C%20Aligarh%2C%20Gonda%20and%20Bareilly.%20The%20process%20of%20setting%20up%20FSLs%20in%20six%20more%20cities%20-%20Basti%2C%20Mirzapur%2C%20Azamgarh%2C%20Banda%2C%20Ayodhya%20and%20Saharanpur%20-%20is%20also%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20hearing%20Mr%20Tiwari's%20plea%20on%20April%2028%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20questioned%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20why%20Ahmed%20and%20Ashraf%2C%20a%20former%20MLA%2C%20were%20paraded%20before%20media%20while%20being%20taken%20to%20a%20hospital%20for%20a%20medical%20checkup%20in%20police%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20counsel%20appearing%20for%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20had%20told%20the%20court%20the%20state%20has%20constituted%20a%20three-member%20commission%20of%20inquiry%20to%20probe%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20special%20investigation%20team%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Police%20is%20also%20investigating%20the%20case%2C%20the%20counsel%20had%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691840760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fusv2tnik_atiq-ahmed-650_625x300_13_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsomeone-is-complicit-supreme-court-on-gangster-politician-atiq-ahmeds-killing-up-encounters-4292536%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20pulled%20up%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20over%20the%20killing%20of%20former%20Lok%20Sabha%20member%20Atiq%20Ahmed%20and%20his%20brother%20Ashraf%20in%20police%20custody%20in%20Prayagraj%20on%20April%2015%2C%20observing%20%26quot%3Bsomeone%20is%20complicit%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsomeone-is-complicit-supreme-court-on-gangster-politician-atiq-ahmeds-killing-up-encounters-4292536%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsomeone-is-complicit-supreme-court-on-gangster-politician-atiq-ahmeds-killing-up-encounters-4292536%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsomeone-is-complicit-supreme-court-on-gangster-politician-atiq-ahmeds-killing-up-encounters-4292536%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kareena%20wishes%20Sara%20with%20a%20cute%20throwback%20pic%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691840752000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102679980%2Cimgsize-37274.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkareena-kapoor-khan-sends-throwback-wishes-to-sara-ali-khan-with-a-cute-throwback-picture-see-inside%2Farticleshow%2F102679924.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102679924.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EKareena%20Kapoor%20Khan%20took%20to%20social%20media%20to%20wish%20Sara%20Ali%20Khan.%20She%20shared%20a%20picture%20of%20Sara%20with%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20and%20a%20picture%20with%20Jeh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkareena-kapoor-khan-sends-throwback-wishes-to-sara-ali-khan-with-a-cute-throwback-picture-see-inside%2Farticleshow%2F102679924.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sudha%20Murty%2C%20Shankar%20Mahadevan%20On%20Panel%20To%20Develop%20New%20NCERT%20Textbooks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EInfosys%20Foundation%20Chairman%20Sudha%20Murty%2C%20music%20maestro%20Shankar%20Mahadevan%2C%20economist%20Sanjeev%20Sanyal%20and%2016%20others%20are%20part%20of%20a%20new%20committee%20constituted%20by%20the%20NCERT%20to%20revise%20textbooks%20according%20to%20the%20new%20curriculum%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2019-member%20National%20Syllabus%20and%20Teaching%20Learning%20Material%20Committee%20(NSTC)%20will%20be%20headed%20by%20National%20Institute%20of%20Educational%20Planning%20and%20Administration%20(NIEPA)%20chancellor%20MC%20Pant%20and%20develop%20textbooks%20for%20classes%203%20to%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20is%20mandated%20to%20prepare%20the%20textbooks%2C%20and%20other%20teaching%20learning%20materials%2C%20which%20will%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20be%20published%20and%20used%20by%20the%20National%20Council%20of%20Educational%20Research%20and%20Training%20(NCERT)%2C%20as%20per%20the%20terms%20of%20reference%2C%20a%20senior%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20NSTC%20will%20be%20assisted%20by%20Curricular%20Area%20Groups%20(CAGs)%20in%20the%20development%20of%20the%20teaching-learning%20material%20for%20each%20curricular%20area.%20These%20groups%20will%20include%20appropriate%20experts%20for%20the%20said%20subject%2C%20and%20will%20be%20formed%20by%20the%20chairperson%20and%20the%20co-Chairperson%20of%20NSTC%2C%20with%20the%20assistance%20of%20NCERT%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20will%20work%20to%20align%20the%20curriculum%20with%20the%20National%20Curriculum%20Framework%20for%20School%20Education%20(NCF-SE)%20developed%20by%20the%20K%20Kasturirangan-led%20steering%20committee%20as%20a%20part%20of%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20final%20NCF-SE%20has%20already%20been%20submitted%20to%20the%20Union%20ministry%20of%20education%2C%20it%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20released%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20The%20draft%20of%20the%20framework%20was%20released%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20is%20co-chaired%20by%20Manjul%20Bhargav%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20mathematics%20at%20Princeton%20University.%20Its%20other%20members%20include%20mathematician%20Sujatha%20Ramdorai%2C%20badminton%20player%20U%20Vimal%20Kumar%2C%20chairperson%20of%20Centre%20for%20Policy%20Studies%20MD%20Srinivas%2C%20and%20chairperson%20of%20Bharatiya%20Bhasha%20Samiti%20Chamu%20Krishna%20Shastry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dropping%20of%20several%20topics%20and%20portions%20from%20NCERT%20textbooks%20in%20May%20triggered%20a%20controversy%2C%20with%20the%20opposition%20blaming%20the%20BJP-led%20Centre%20for%20%26quot%3Bwhitewashing%20with%20vengeance%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20controversy%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20while%20the%20changes%20made%20as%20part%20of%20a%20rationalisation%20exercise%20were%20notified%2C%20some%20of%20the%20controversial%20deletions%20were%20not%20mentioned.%20This%20led%20to%20allegations%20about%20a%20bid%20to%20delete%20these%20portions%20surreptitiously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20NCERT%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20omissions%20in%20the%20textbooks%20may%20have%20been%20unintentional%2C%20they%20declined%20to%20reverse%20the%20deletions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCERT%20said%20the%20removals%20were%20made%20based%20on%20the%20recommendations%20provided%20by%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691840700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fqlqt0ih8_sudha-murthy_625x300_09_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsudha-murty-shankar-mahadevan-on-panel-to-develop-new-ncert-textbooks-4292611%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Infosys%20Foundation%20Chairman%20Sudha%20Murty%2C%20music%20maestro%20Shankar%20Mahadevan%2C%20economist%20Sanjeev%20Sanyal%20and%2016%20others%20are%20part%20of%20a%20new%20committee%20constituted%20by%20the%20NCERT%20to%20revise%20textbooks%20according%20to%20the%20new%20curriculum%2C%20officials%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsudha-murty-shankar-mahadevan-on-panel-to-develop-new-ncert-textbooks-4292611%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsudha-murty-shankar-mahadevan-on-panel-to-develop-new-ncert-textbooks-4292611%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsudha-murty-shankar-mahadevan-on-panel-to-develop-new-ncert-textbooks-4292611%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20left%20my%20life%20in%20DC%20to%20live%20in%20a%20400-square-foot%20tiny%20home%20near%20Tampa.%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20have%20more%20space%20and%20I'm%20saving%20money%20so%20I%20don't%20regret%20it.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%20A%20selfie%20of%20Stefanie%20Mortenson%20next%20to%20her%20eESCAPE%20One%20XL%2FWide.%20tiny%20home%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d3ea19ec14ba0019f38f2a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStefanie%20Mortenson%20traded%20her%20life%20in%20Virginia%20for%20a%20%24159%2C000%20tiny%20home%20near%20Tampa%2C%20Florida.%3Cp%3EStefanie%20Mortenson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EStefanie%20Mortenson%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E53-year-old%20HR%20director%2C%20moved%20from%20Virginia%20to%20a%20tiny%20home%20near%20Tampa%2C%20Florida%20in%20May.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHer%C2%A0396-square-foot%20dwelling%20at%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiny-home-community-florida-nearly-sold-out-photos-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEscape%20Tampa%20Bay%20Village's%C2%A0tiny%C2%A0home%C2%A0community%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Ecost%20her%20%24159%2C000.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMortenson%20says%20she's%20saving%20money%20and%20feels%20like%20she%20has%20more%20space%20compared%20to%20her%20previous%20Virginia%20apartment.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20an%20interview%20with%20Stefanie%20Mortenson%2C%20a%2053-year-old%20HR%20director%20who%20moved%20from%20Virginia%20to%20Escape%20Tampa%20Bay%20Village's%20The%20Oaks%20community%2C%20a%20tiny%20home%20neighborhood%20near%20Tampa%2C%20Florida.%C2%A0The%20interview%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20priorities%20changed%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201998%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20Alexandria%2C%20Virginia%20about%2010%20miles%20from%20Washington%2C%20DC%20for%20a%20better%20career%20opportunity.%20I%20was%20a%20month%20shy%20of%2025%20years%20in%20Virginia%20and%20working%20at%20the%20US%20Senate%20Federal%20Credit%20Union%20%E2%80%94%20where%20I'm%20currently%20the%20director%20of%20human%20resources%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0when%20I%20moved%20to%20my%20new%20tiny%20home%20in%20Escape%20Tampa%20Bay%20Village's%20The%20Oaks%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20been%20looking%20to%20move%20somewhere%20on%20the%20coastline.%20And%20living%20near%20Washington%2C%20DC%20was%20very%20expensive.%20I%20wanted%20to%20own%20a%20home%20but%20the%20cost%20was%20absolutely%20ridiculous.%20I%20got%20tired%20of%20the%20traffic.%20I%20got%20tired%20of%20hearing%20my%20neighbors%20all%20the%20time.%20I%20was%20doing%20everything%20not%20to%20work%20from%20home%20even%20though%20I%20could%20just%20because%20it%20was%20too%20noisy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20walls%20started%20coming%20in%20on%20me%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20eESCAPE%20One%20XL%2FWide%20at%20the%20tiny%20home%20community%20near%20Tampa%2C%20Florida%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d3fc054dd2b50019c25c1c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221150%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20May%2C%2053-year-old%20Stefanie%20Mortenson%20moved%20from%20her%20apartment%20in%20Virginia%20to%20396-square-foot%20tiny%20home%20in%20%C2%A0Escape%20Tampa%20Bay%20Village's%20The%20Oaks%20neighborhood.%3Cp%3E%20Escape%2FRoy%20Hawkes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20turned%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20minimalism.%20And%20these%20tiny%20homes%20were%20very%20intriguing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20first%20found%20this%20particular%20neighborhood%20after%20googling%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fone-250000-home-left-popular-tiny-home-community-near-tampa-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etiny%20home%20developments%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20in%20May%202020.%20When%20presales%20opened%20in%20March%202023%2C%20I%20literally%20got%20up%20at%205%20a.m.%20At%20around%206%20or%207%20a.m.%2C%20it%20opened%20and%20I%20bought%20my%20house%20based%20on%20a%20video%20of%20the%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20an%20open%20house%20a%20few%20weeks%20after.%20So%20I%20flew%20down%20to%20see%20and%20start%20taking%20measurements%20of%20my%20new%20396-square-foot%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20two%20lofts.%20One%20is%20five%20feet%2C%20one-inch%20tall%20while%20the%20other%20is%20only%20four%20feet%2C%20five%20inches%20tall.%20When%20I%20first%20entered%20my%20unit%20and%20sat%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20shorter%20loft%2C%20I%20asked%20myself%2C%20%26quot%3BCan%20I%20do%20this%3F%26quot%3B%20But%20I%20realized%20I'm%20only%20going%20to%20be%20sleeping%20there.%20Once%20I%20sat%20in%20the%20space%20and%20thought%20about%20it%2C%20everything%20was%20fine.%20Now%2C%20one%20loft%20is%20my%20office%20for%20remote%20work%20and%20the%20other%20is%20my%20bedroom.%20It%20worked%20out%20perfectly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20sold%20most%20of%20my%20furniture%20before%20I%20came%20down%20here%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inside%20the%20eESCAPE%20One%20XL%2FWide%20with%20a%20loft%2C%20kitchen%2C%20large%20windows%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d3fc23ec14ba0019f3a7d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMortenson's%20%24159%2C000%20tiny%20home%20has%20two%20lofts%2C%20a%20bathroom%2C%20a%20kitchen%2C%20a%20living%20room%2C%20and%20an%20outdoor%20deck.%20The%20neighborhood%20also%20has%20amenities%20like%20a%20pool%2C%20park%2C%20and%20additional%20storage.%3Cp%3EEscape%2FRoy%20Hawkes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20moved%20into%20my%20house%20in%20May%2C%20I%20realized%20I%20still%20had%20too%20much%20stuff.%20So%20I've%20been%20slowly%20but%20surely%20getting%20rid%20of%20it.%20I'm%20actually%20enjoying%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20starting%20anew%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20ways%20and%20I've%20had%20to%20be%20more%20creative.%20The%20furniture%20I%20ended%20up%20buying%20has%20dual%20purposes%2C%20like%20a%20couch%20with%20built-in%20storage.%20But%20it%20feels%20like%20I%20have%20more%20space%20than%20I%20did%20at%20my%20650-square-foot%20Virginia%20apartment.%20Here%2C%20the%20space%20is%20better%20utilized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%2C%20the%20community%20is%20a%20pretty%20and%20calming%20place%20to%20live.%20You%20don't%20come%20in%20here%20thinking%20it's%20a%20mobile%20home%20park.%20It's%20more%20upscale%20than%20that.%20And%20the%20homes%20are%20too%20%E2%80%94%20they%20look%20higher-end%20than%20some%20of%20the%20mobile%20homes%20I've%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20old%20apartment%20had%20two%20glass%20sliding%20doors%20and%20a%20tiny%20window%20in%20the%20bedroom.%20Here%2C%20these%20units%20have%20a%20ton%20of%20windows.%20It's%20nice%20looking%20out%20and%20seeing%20the%20park%20with%20trees%20and%20Spanish%20moss.%20I%20see%20it%20every%20day%20and%20it's%20still%20lovely.%20That%20feeling%20hasn't%20faded%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20it%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20home%20will%20be%20paid%20off%20before%20I%20retire%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20two%20upstairs%20lofts%20in%20escape's%20lot%2026.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d530b7005c4a00183d6d9e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEscape%2FRoy%20Hawkes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%