20monsoon%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20Bill%2C%20which%20gives%20the%20Union%20government%20control%20over%20the%20postings%20and%20transfers%20of%20bureaucrats%20in%20Delhi%2C%20was%20opposed%20by%20the%20INDIA%20coalition%20of%20opposition%20parties.%20It%20will%20replace%20the%20ordinance%20promulgated%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20May%20this%20year%20to%20create%20the%20National%20Capital%20Civil%20Service%20Authority%20to%20administer%20the%20transfer%20and%20posting%20of%20bureaucrats%20serving%20the%20Delhi%20government.%20The%20ordinance%20itself%20was%20passed%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%20said%20the%20national%20capital%20territory%20government%20has%20legislative%20power%20over%20bureaucrats%20in%20all%20departments%20other%20than%20public%20order%2C%20police%20and%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%20has%20been%20roundly%20criticised%20by%20activists%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwill-the-data-protection-law-empower-the-public%5C%22%3Esay%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20will%20enable%20surveillance%2C%20will%20not%20stop%20personal%20data%20collection%20by%20Big%20Tech%20companies%2C%20reduce%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20RTI%20law%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fdigital-personal-data-protection-bill-adverse-impact-press-freedom-editors-guild%5C%22%3Ehinder%20press%20freedom%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20two%20other%20Bills%20that%20have%20been%20signed%20by%20the%20president%2C%20the%20Registration%20of%20Births%20and%20Deaths%20(Amendment)%20Act%20will%20make%20digital%20birth%20certificates%20the%20only%20conclusive%20age%20proof.%20This%20law%20has%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fregistration-of-births-deaths-aadhaar-voter-id%5C%22%3Esparked%20concerns%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20surveillance%20and%20that%20it%20may%20impede%20the%20registration%20of%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jan%20Vishwas%20(Amendment%20of%20Provisions)%20Act%20decriminalises%20minor%20offences%20through%20amendments%20in%20183%20provisions%20of%2042%20Acts.%20It%20converts%20several%20fines%20to%20penalties%2C%20removing%20the%20need%20for%20prosecutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691839216000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25191458%2FH20230620133706.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbills-on-data-protection-and-delhi-services-among-four-granted-assent-by-president%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20four%20Bills%20that%20have%20been%20cleared%20by%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20are%20the%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%2C%20the%20Registration%20of%20Births%20and%20Deaths%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%20the%20Jan%20Vishwas%20(Amendment%20of%20Provisions)%20Bill%2C%20and%20the%20Government%20of%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%20(Amendment)%20Bill.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbills-on-data-protection-and-delhi-services-among-four-granted-assent-by-president%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ISIS%20module%20case%3A%20Court%20remands%20seventh%20accused%20to%20NIA%20custody%20till%20Aug%2018%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691839149000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102679529%2Cimgsize-23512.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Fisis-module-case-court-remands-seventh-accused-to-nia-custody-till-aug-18%2Farticleshow%2F102679327.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20the%20probe%20agency%2C%20Nachan%20was%20allegedly%20actively%20involved%20in%20promoting%20terrorist%20activities%20of%20the%20designated%20foreign%20terrorist%20organisation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canon