0BJP's%20audacious%20bid%20to%20supplant%20our%20identity%20with%20Hindi%20will%20be%20opposed%20resolutely%26quot%3B%2C%20adding%20a%20hashtag%20to%20stop%20Hindi%20imposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20introduced%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20the%20three%20Bills%20aimed%20at%20giving%20justice%20and%20protecting%20the%20rights%20given%20to%20Indian%20citizens%20by%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntroducing%20the%20bills%2C%20he%20said%20the%20soul%20of%20these%20three%20new%20laws%20will%20be%20to%20protect%20all%20the%20rights%20given%20by%20the%20Constitution%20to%20the%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20said%20that%20the%20three%20bills%20-%20The%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%20Bill%2C%202023%3B%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Sakhshya%20Bill%2C%202023-%20fulfil%20a%20vow%20outlined%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20his%20Independence%20Day%20address%20to%20end%20all%20signs%20of%20slavery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691838720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2F08fub0b8_mk-stalin-1200_625x300_16_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdmk-objects-to-hindi-names-of-criminal-laws-to-be-revamped-under-new-bill-4292065%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ruling%20DMK%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20opposed%20the%20central%20government's%20Hindi%20names%20for%20the%20bills%20introduced%20in%20Parliament%20on%20Friday%20to%20replace%20British-era%20criminal%20laws.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdmk-objects-to-hindi-names-of-criminal-laws-to-be-revamped-under-new-bill-4292065%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A