he%20pandemic%20began%2C%20it%20was%20as%20simple%20as%20giving%20my%20supervisor%20a%20heads%20up%20that%20I'd%20start%20working%20from%20outside%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20apartment%20lease%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20ended%20in%20March%2C%20I%20opted%20to%20let%20it%20go%20rather%20than%20renew%20it%2C%20as%20my%20rent%20cost%20%242%2C100%20a%20month.%20Now%2C%20my%20total%20expenses%20range%20from%20%241%2C500%20to%20%242%2C500%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20four%20life%20lessons%20I've%20learned%20from%20my%20time%20as%20a%20digital%20nomad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou're%20going%20to%20need%20to%20get%20active%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Daniel%20Ferrer%20at%20the%20Pamplona%20Bull%20Run%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cb43f5ce6977001984fc57%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221350%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDaniel%20Ferrer%20at%20the%20Pamplona%20Bull%20Run%3Cp%3EDaniel%20Ferrer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3EThe%20Pamplona%20Bull%20Run%20was%20the%20most%20adrenaline-filled%20experience%20of%20my%20life.%20While%20I%20was%20running%2C%20I%20was%20constantly%20checking%20over%20my%20arm%20and%20making%20sure%20a%20bull%20wasn't%20right%20behind%20me%2C%20about%20to%20trample%20me.%3Cp%3EAnd%20I%20was%20there%20all%20because%20of%20a%20German%20guy%20I%20happened%20to%20meet%20in%20Kuala%20Lumpur.%20We%20ended%20up%20hanging%20out%20every%20night%20in%20the%20Jacuzzi%20in%20our%20hostel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20saw%2C%20via%20Instagram%2C%20that%20I%20was%20in%20Europe%20two%20months%20later%2C%20he%20told%20me%3A%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%20in%20Pamplona%20for%20the%20Bull%20Run.%20Come%20meet%20up%20if%20you%20want%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20did.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%2C%20and%20Instagram%20in%20particular%2C%20has%20been%20a%20critical%20part%20of%20my%20travels.%20Often%2C%20I%20have%20found%20%E2%80%94%20just%20by%20actively%20posting%20photos%20and%20videos%20%E2%80%94%20that%20I'm%20in%20the%20same%20city%20as%20another%20traveler%20I%20met%20two%20countries%20ago%2C%20so%20why%20not%20go%20ahead%20and%20grab%20drinks%20and%20dinner%20together%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20have%20to%20get%20used%20to%20constantly%20saying%20goodbye%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221283%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Daniel%20Ferrer%20at%20Oslo%20Pride%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cb48a795fe1f0019df84f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22962%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDaniel%20Ferrer%20at%20Oslo%20Pride%3Cp%3EDaniel%20Ferrer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20four%20months%20of%20traveling%2C%20I've%20made%20more%20friends%20than%20I%20did%20in%20four%20years%20of%20living%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hit%20it%20off%20with%20one%20guy%20in%20Bangkok.%20Every%20night%2C%20we%20made%20a%20point%20of%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20we're%20having%20dinner%20together%2C%20and%20we're%20gonna%20go%20catch%20up%20on%20our%20day.%26quot%3B%20We%20became%20best%20friends%20in%20that%20month.%20When%20this%20guy%20invited%20me%20to%20come%20up%20to%20Norway%20for%20Oslo%20Pride%2C%20I%20said%20sure.%20And%20we%20wound%20up%20having%20a%20great%20time%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%C2%A0lifestyle%2C%20there's%20a%20good%20dance%20you'll%20see%20everyone%20again.%20You%20just%20have%20to%20get%20used%20to%20constantly%20saying%20hello%20and%20goodbye.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAirports%20take%20up%20a%20big%20chunk%20of%20a%20digital%20nomad's%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGet%20used%20to%20spending%20a%20lot%20of%20your%20time%20in%20airports%2C%20and%20don't%20party%20hard%20the%20night%20before%20you%20fly%20%E2%80%94%20I've%20missed%20two%20flights%20that%20way%20already.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGo%20in%20on%20a%20local%20SIM%20ca