%20hiring%20people%20you%20can%20trust%20to%20get%20their%20job%20done%20from%20their%20couch%20%E2%80%94%20or%20wherever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20do%2C%20they%20could%20be%20more%20likely%20to%20stick%20around%20for%20the%20long%20run.%20Deloitte%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-execs-would-quit-if-mandated-back-to-office-2023-8%5C%22%3Efound%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20firm%20return-to-office%20mandates%20could%20hurt%20retention%2C%20with%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20700%20executives%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.deloitte.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fpages%2Fabout-deloitte%2Farticles%2Fpress-releases%2Fdeloitte-survey-financial-services-leaders-working-remote-hybrid-would-leave-if-required-to-work-in-office-full-time.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurveyed%3C%2Fa%3E%20saying%20that%20they'd%20likely%20leave%20their%20current%20roles%20if%20they%20were%20required%20to%20come%20back%20in%20five%20days%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS0090261623000256%3Fvia%253Dihub%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epaper%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20the%20research%20journal%20Organizational%20Dynamics%20by%20professors%20from%20Pepperdine%20University%2C%20University%20of%20New%20Hampshire%2C%20Simon%20Fraser%20University%2C%20and%20University%20of%20Calgary%20concludes%20that%20%26quot%3Bchanging%20the%20work%20arrangement%20alone%20is%20not%20a%20panacea%20for%20solving%20an%20organization's%20problems.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEither%20you%20trust%20your%20employees%20are%20working%20or%20you%20don't%20and%2C%20if%20you%20don't%2C%20you%20have%20a%20culture%20issue%20that%20is%20far%20bigger%20than%20the%20question%20of%20virtual%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Lucy%20Gilson%2C%20dean%20of%20the%20Paul%20College%20of%20Business%20and%20Economics%20at%20the%20University%20of%20New%20Hampshire%2C%20told%20the%20researchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20speaking%20with%20thousands%20of%20firms%2C%20Stanford%20University%20economics%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhybrid-working-model-wfh-work-from-home-policy-office-trends-2023-7%5C%22%3Eprofessor%20Nicholas%20Bloom%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20people%20haven't%20been%20goofing%20off%20at%20home%20any%20more%20than%20in%20the%20office%20%E2%80%94%20which%20may%20run%20contrary%20to%20what%20some%20companies%20believe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20do%20find%20in%20our%20data%20is%20that%20what%20they%20are%20doing%20is%20different%2C%20and%20the%20big%20driver%20is%20the%20value%20and%20the%20opportunities%20for%20leisure%20at%20home%20are%20much%20higher%2C%26quot%3B%20Bloom%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%20will%20take%20breaks%20whether%20they're%20in%20the%20office%20or%20at%20home.%20But%20being%20able%20to%20run%20out%20and%20get%20groceries%20or%20take%20a%20midday%20workout%20while%20working%20from%20home%20could%20be%20more%20valuable%20to%20employees%20than%20just%20scrolling%20through%20their%20phones%20during%20an%20in-office%20break.%20And%20that%20could%20pay%20off%20for%20both%20firms%20and%20workers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20the%20whole%20saying%20about%20working%20from%20home%2C%20'shirking%20from%20home%2C'%20or%20working%20remotely%2C%20'remotely%20working%2C'%26quot%3B%20Bloom%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20turns%20out%20that's%20just%20not%20true.%20If%20you%20look%20in%20the%20data%2C%20either%20firm%20level%20studies%2C%20or%20just%20look%20at%20the%20whole%20US%20economy%2C%20we're%20basically%20on%20the%20pre-pandemic%20growth%20trend%20and%20we've%20seen%20five%20times%20increase%20in%20work%20from%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20there%20are%20concerns%20about%20how%20much%20people%20are%20getting%20done%20at%20home.%20Recent%20research%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fare-remote-jobs-more-productive-work-life-balance-return-office-2023-8%5C%22%3Eindicated%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20workers%20might%20be%20more%20productive%20if%20they%20come%20into%20the%20office%20some%20days%20rather%20than%20work%20at%20home%20full%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Chris%20Bailey%2C%20who's%20written%20three%20books%20on%20productivity%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20both%20work%20and%20life%2C%20%26quot%3Bproductivity%20is%20really%20about%20one%20thing%20and%20one%20thing%20only%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20is%20intentionality.%26quot%3B%20If%20you're%20intentional%20in%20what%20you%20want%20to%20get%20done%20and%20accomplish%20that%2C%20you're%20productive%20in%20Bailey's%20eyes%3B%20that%20could%20extend%20to%20taking%20a%20midday%20shower%20and%20letting%20your%20mind%20wander%20to%20what%20needs%20to%20get%20done%2C%20setting%20you%20up%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20might%20come%20up%20against%20how%20we%20traditionally%20view%20productivity%20at%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20really%20bad%20at%20measuring%20our%20productivity%2C%26quot%3B%20Bailey%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20just%20a%20simple%20truth%20about%20knowledge%20work.%20Because%20we%20feel%20more%20productive%20when%20we're%20busier%2C%20even%20if%20we're%20just%20answering%20email%20all%20day%20long%20or%20doing%20busy%20work%20that%20is%20the%20work%20equivalent%20of%20shuffling%20the%20deck%20chairs%20around.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESaving%20money%20on%20office%20leases%20to%20invest%20in%20trust%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusiness-owner-burnout-took-sabbatical-treat-anxiety-exhaustion-2021-4%5C%22%3EFor%20Eitzen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20decision%20to%20part%20ways%20with%20his%20lease%20was%20a%20no-brainer.%20Pre-pandemic%2C%20Eitzen%20had%20three%20offices%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20including%20a%20warehouse%20and%20modern%20spaces%20for%20sales%20staff%20%E2%80%94%20about%20an%20hour%20outside%20Seattle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPre-pandemic%2C%20he%20envisioned%20staff%20working%20away%20in%20a%20sleek%20office%2C%20tapping%20at%20keyboards%20and%20hitting%20the%20phones%20to%20pull%20in%20new%20clients.%20But%20after%20he%20noticed%20barely%20anybody%20was%20coming%20into%20the%20offices%2C%20he%20felt%20his%20employees%20would%20be%20more%20productive%20if%20they%20worked%20where%20they%20were%20comfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20dawned%20on%20me%20when%20we%20started%20facing%20near%20disaster%20as%20an%20events-centric%20company%20that%20company%20culture%20was%20like%20compound%20interest%2C%26quot%3B%20Eitzen%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20keep%20investing%20in%20it%2C%20little%20by%20little%2C%20and%20even%20though%20it%20doesn't%20seem%20like%20much%20at%20first%2C%20it%20grows%20exponentially.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrust%20works%20the%20same%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BWe%20invested%20in%20trust%2C%20built%20trust%2C%20little%20by%20little.%20We%20were%20transparent%20with%20numbers%2C%20transparent%20with%20goals%20and%20also%20our%20personal%20desires%20for%20the%20company%20as%20founders.%20We%20were%20honest%20about%20when%20we%20were%20having%20bad%20days%20and%20we%20celebrated%20the%20good%20ones.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20laying%20off%20a%20few%20staff%20who%20had%20previously%20worked%20with%20the%20company's%20physical%20photo%20booths%2C%20what%20he%20found%20was%20the%20remaining%20staff%20were%20even%20more%20productive%20at%20home%20based%20on%20revenue%20and%20overall%20attitudes.%20He's%20confident%20he'll%20scale%20the%20company%20more%20now%20that%20everything%20is%20remote%2C%20and%20costs%20are%20down%20while%20staff%20are%20thriving.%20That's%20why%20Eitzen%20is%20making%20remote%20work%20permanent.%20In%20fact%2C%20he's%20already%20gearing%20up%20to%20move%20to%20Spain%20and%20Italy%20for%20a%20few%20months%20while%20working%20remotely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEitzen%20said%20he's%20giving%20his%20employees%20more%20freedom%20to%20work%20how%20they%20want.%20It's%20just%20the%20right%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20say%20in-person%20is%20the%20only%20way%20to%20work%2C%20nor%20would%20I%20say%20that%20virtual%20works%20for%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20Eitzen%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20really%20just%20have%20to%20be%20smart%20about%20it%20and%20find%20a%20good%20balance%20for%20the%20people%20you've%20bought%20on%20your%20team.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20boss%20or%20worker%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20keep%20remote%20work%20functional%3F%20Contact%20these%20reporters%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajkaplan%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejkaplan%40insider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ansheidlower%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ensheidlower%40insider.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-from-home-remote-work-forever-boss-trust-employees-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691836801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d65d28005c4a00183e2101%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-from-home-remote-work-forever-boss-trust-employees-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Letting%20workers%20go%20play%20pickleball%20or%20run%20errands%20during%20the%20day%20might%20be%20more%20valuable%20for%20both%20bosses%20and%20employees.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nsheidlower%40insider.com%20(Noah%20Sheidlower%2CJuliana%20Kaplan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-from-home-remote-work-forever-boss-trust-employees-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rani%20Rampal%20excluded%