C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20CEO%20David%20Solomon%20speaks%20at%20the%20bank's%20investor%20day%20this%20February.%3Cp%3EBRENDAN%20MCDERMID%20%2F%20REUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDavid%20Solomon%20was%20criticized%20of%20%26quot%3Bblatant%20ignorance%20and%20disrespect%26quot%3B%20at%20a%20college%20event.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Goldman%20Sachs%20CEO%20discussed%20divestment%20issues%20with%20students%20at%20his%20alma%20mater%20Hamilton%20College.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Insider.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EStudents%20at%20David%20Solomon's%20alma%20mater%20have%20accused%20the%20Goldman%20Sachs%20CEO%20of%20having%20%26quot%3Bblatant%20ignorance%20and%20disrespect%26quot%3B%20during%20a%20conversation%20about%20fossil%20fuel%20divestment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20seniors%20at%20New%20York's%20Hamilton%20College%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthespectator.medium.com%2Flte-divestment-disillusionment-and-disrespect-our-experience-with-david-solomon-85b83fc9255e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20a%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20accusing%20the%20executive%20of%20%26quot%3Bbelittling%26quot%3B%20them%20during%20a%20discussion%20about%20the%20university's%20climate%20change%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESolomon%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hamilton.edu%2Fnews%2Fstory%2Fdavid-solomon-goldman-sachs-ceo-chair-hamilton-board-trustees%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Egraduated%20from%20the%20private%20liberal%20arts%20college%20in%201984%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20attending%20a%20networking%20event%20at%20the%20college%20in%20March%20this%20year%20when%20the%20students%20challenged%20him%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20divestment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20says%20that%20Solomon%20was%20speaking%20to%20%26quot%3Ba%20group%20of%20six%20or%20so%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20who%20%26quot%3Bwere%20all%20non-male%2C%20and%20at%20least%20half%20were%20people%20of%20color.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20adds%20that%20throughout%20the%20discussion%2C%20Solomon's%20attitude%20and%20behavior%20toward%20the%20students%20came%20from%20a%20%26quot%3Bposition%20of%20power.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3EDespite%20knowing%20nothing%20about%20us%20and%20our%20roles%20in%20our%20communities%20and%20history%20of%20activist%20work%2C%20Solomon%20claimed%20he%20does%20more%20in%20a%20week%20to%20help%20climate%20change%20than%20we%20will%20ever%20do%20in%20our%20entire%20lives.%20When%20we%20asked%20him%20to%20elaborate%2C%20he%20attributed%20his%20%26quot%3Bcapital%20accumulation%26quot%3B%20and%20position%20of%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20read.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20also%20claims%20that%20Solomon%20pointed%20to%20the%20group%2C%20claiming%20that%20they%20must%20have%20benefitted%20from%20a%20financial%20aid.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20we%20all%20looked%20shocked%20at%20the%20claim%2C%20he%20quickly%20backtracked%2C%20citing%20the%20statistic%20that%20something%20like%2080%25%20of%20Hamilton%20students%20are%20on%20some%20kind%20of%20financial%20aid%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20also%20said%20Solomon%20suggested%20fossil%20fuel%20divestment%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bstupid%20movement%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20that%20the%20university%20likely%20had%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hamilton.edu%2Fendowment%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigher%20exposure%20to%20fossil%20fuels%20than%20it%20claimed%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20alleged%20that%20Solomon%20also%20called%20them%20hypocrites%20for%20driving%20cars%20and%20using%20electricity%20while%20supporting%20divestment%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20told%20them%20they%20would%20%26quot%