ion%20was%20defeated%20by%20a%20voice%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20a%20Short%20Duration%20Discussion%20notice%20was%20accepted%20to%20discuss%20law-and-order%20issues%20in%20Manipur.%20Such%20discussions%20are%20usually%20taken%20up%20for%20up%20to%20two%20and%20a%20half%20hours.%20However%2C%20due%20to%20disruptions%2C%20the%20House%20was%20adjourned%20after%20just%20a%20minute%20of%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdjournment%20motions%20are%20filed%20to%20suspend%20existing%20business%20for%20the%20day%20and%20discuss%20a%20matter%20of%20urgent%20importance.%20In%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20more%20than%20250%20such%20notices%20were%20filed%20to%20discuss%20the%20law-and-order%20situation%20in%20Manipur.%20However%2C%20none%20of%20these%20were%20accepted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20title%3D%5C%22Page%202%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeputy%20Speaker%20not%20elected%20with%20less%20than%20a%20year%20of%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20remaining%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20title%3D%5C%22Page%202%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20has%20not%20elected%20a%20Deputy%20Speaker%20as%20it%20enters%20the%20final%20year%20of%20its%20term.%20This%20is%20the%20longest%20time%20that%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20has%20functioned%20without%20a%20Deputy%20Speaker%20(1%2C517%20days).%20The%20Constitution%20mandates%20Lok%20Sabha%20to%20choose%20a%20Speaker%20and%20a%20Deputy%20Speaker%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F12133935%2FScreenshot-2023-08-12-at-1.38.58-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F12133935%2FScr