20be%20created%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fassam-cm-himanta-biswa-sarmas-jalukbari-constituency-among-30-seats-to-be-altered-by-proposed-delimitation%2Farticleshow%2F101261965.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feci.gov.in%2Ffiles%2Ffile%2F15218-eci-publishes-final-delimitation-order-for-assembly-parliamentary-constituencies-of-state-of-assam-after-extensive-consultations-with-stakeholders%2F%5C%22%3Efinal%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20did%20not%20further%20change%20any%20constituency%20boundaries%2C%20but%20renamed%2019%20assembly%20constituencies%20and%20one%20parliamentary%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssam%20chief%20minister%20and%20BJP%20leader%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhimantabiswa%2Fstatus%2F1672188658731061249%5C%22%3Ehad%20earlier%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20if%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20draft%20proposal%20was%20approved%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpeople%20of%20Assam%E2%80%9D%20would%20have%20a%20greater%20say%20in%20their%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20this%20draft%20is%20approved%20and%20comes%20into%20reality%2C%20then%20the%20people%20of%20Assam%20will%20hold%20prominence%20in%20102%20constituencies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20during%20a%20speech%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Lakhimpur%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAssam%20should%20not%20be%20taken%20over%20by%20unfamiliar%20persons%2C%20and%20for%20that%20we%20worked%20religiously%20to%20protect%20%3Cem%3Ejati%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5Bcommunity%5D%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emati%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5Bland%5D%2C%20and%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ebheti%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5Bfoundation%5D%2C%20so%20as%20to%20retain%20the%20political%20power%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20our%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fexplainer-the-politics-behind-assam-govts-decision-to-merge-districts-just-before-delimitation%5C%22%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20Gerrymandering%20of%20Assam%20Districts%20Puts%20Identity%20Politics%20at%20the%20Centre%20of%20Its%202024%20Strategy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20and%20the%20delimitation%20proposal%20have%20been%20criticised%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20weaken%20the%20representation%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Bengali-origin%20Muslim%20community%2C%20who%20are%20often%20vilified%20as%20illegal%20immigrants%20from%20neighbouring%20Muslim-majority%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20All%20India%20United%20Democratic%20Front%20(AIUDF)%20party%2C%20whose%20primary%20voter%20base%20is%20among%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Bengali-origin%20Muslims%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fassam-will-have-fewer-muslim-majority-constituencies-say-opposition-leaders%2Farticle67012017.ece%5C%22%3Ehas%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20will%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20Muslim-majority%20assembly%20constituencies%20in%20the%20state%20from%2029%20to%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20constituencies%20which%20always%20elect%20legislators%20from%20the%20minority%20community%20have%20also%20been%20reserved%20for%20either%20Scheduled%20Caste%20(SC)%20or%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(ST)%20contestants%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20delimitation%20uses%20data%20from%20the%202001%20census%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%202011%20one%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fassam-will-have-fewer-muslim-majority-constituencies-say-opposition-leaders%2Farticle67012017.ece%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20means%20that%20increases%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Muslim%20population%20will%20not%20factor%20into%20revising%20the%20nature%20of%20existing%20SC%20and%20ST%20constituencies%2C%20thus%20protecting%20them%20from%20being%20de-reserved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delimitation%20exercise%20will%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20ST%20assembly%20constituencies%20in%20Assam%20from%2016%20to%2019%20and%20SC%20assembly%20constituencies%20from%20eight%20to%20nine.%20Two%20parliamentary%20constituencies%20have%20also%20been%20reserved%20for%20STs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAIUDF%20chief%20Badruddin%20Ajmal%20said%20that%20his%20party%20will%20suffer%20heavy%20losses%20if%20the%20proposed%20draft%20was%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20planning%20has%20been%20done%20with%20BJP%20as%20the%20mastermind%20with%20the%20target%20of%20reducing%20%5Bthe%20impact%20of%5D%20Muslim%20votes%20to%20the%20extent%20possible.%20The%20way%20Himanta%20has%20done%20this%20along%20with%20Amit%20Shah%20is%20such%20that%20Assam%20can%20have%20only%20two%20parties%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20that%20no%20other%20party%20can%20be%20in%20the%20middle%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fassam-delimitation-oppn-nrc-census-bjp-8682526%2F%5C%22%3Ealleged%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691829214000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F12132556%2FAssam-Legislative-Assembly-II.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Felection-commission-releases-final-assam-delimitation-order%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20did%20not%20further%20change%20constituency%20boundaries%20from%20its%20June%20draft%20order%2C%20which%20was%20criticised%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20reduce%20the%20representation%20of%20the%20state's%20Muslim%20community.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Felection-commission-releases-final-assam-delimitation-order%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%