0To%20keep%20the%20pot%20boiling%2C%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20with%20the%20passage%20of%20time%2C%20a%20negotiated%20settlement%20might%20be%20possible%20is%20patently%20contrary%20to%20the%20lessons%20of%20recent%20history.%20Some%20necessary%20accommodation%20to%20address%20the%20sense%20of%20disquiet%20%E2%80%93%20legitimate%20or%20otherwise%20%E2%80%93%20of%20the%20majority%20makes%20sense%2C%20but%20continuing%20down%20that%20path%20to%20rewrite%20history%20will%20be%20disastrous%20for%20the%20idea%20of%20India%20%E2%80%93%20that%20we%20the%20people%2C%20captured%20in%20the%20Indian%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderstandably%2C%20there%20is%20talk%20amongst%20minority%20citizens%20about%20what%20short-term%20and%20long-term%20communication%20strategies%20to%20adopt%20for%20a%20working%20relationship%20with%20the%20government%20and%20the%20majority%20they%20claim%20to%20represent.%20Periodically%20some%20people%20have%20taken%20the%20initiative%20to%20join%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmuslim-intellectuals-mohan-bhagwat-dialogue-or-monologues%5C%22%3Edialogue%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20high%20functionaries%20of%20the%20government%20and%20leadership%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20with%20uncertain%20results%20beyond%20photo%20ops%20and%20well-meaning%20press%20statements.%20Others%20have%20gone%20further%20to%20secure%20membership%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20have%20even%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fonly-one-party-wins-when-indian-muslims-defend-the-bjp%5C%22%3Enominated%20to%20the%20Upper%20House%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmuslims-must-dialogue-with-all-indians-except-those-who-dream-of-their-disenfranchisement%5C%22%3EMuslims%20Must%20Dialogue%20with%20All%20Indians%2C%20Except%20Those%20Who%20Dream%20of%20Their%20Disenfranchisem