ng%20to%20the%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20the%20top%20court%20observed%20that%20there%20has%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Charmony%20and%20comity%E2%80%9D%20between%20communities%20and%20asked%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20constitute%20a%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20the%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20made%20these%20observations%20during%20the%20resumed%20hearing%20of%20a%20plea%20seeking%20action%20against%20those%20who%20called%20for%20the%20social%20and%20economic%20boycott%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%20following%20the%20violence%20in%20Nuh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShaheen%20Abdulla%2C%20who%20filed%20the%20plea%2C%20relied%20on%20a%20video%20in%20which%20an%20organisation%20on%20August%202%20warned%20residents%20and%20shopkeepers%20of%20boycott%20if%20they%20continue%20to%20employ%20any%20Muslims.%20The%20video%20was%20from%20a%20neighbourhood%20in%20Hisar%2C%20Haryana%20and%20police%20officials%20could%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20stated%20that%20such%20calls%20not%20only%20%E2%80%9Cdemonise%20communities%20and%20openly%20call%20for%20violence%E2%80%9D%20but%20also%20would%20%E2%80%9Cinevitably%20lead%20to%20communal%20disharmony%20and%20violence%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fcall-for-boycott-of-muslims-unacceptable-hate-speech-needs-to-end-supreme-court%2Farticleshow%2F102659631.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20S.V.N.%20Bhatti%20asked%20additional%20solicitor%20general%20K.M.%20Nataraj%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Centre%2C%20to%20seek%20instructions%20and%20inform%20it%20about%20the%20committee%20by%20August%2018.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20to%20be%20harmony%20and%20comity%20between%20the%20communities.%20All%20the%20communities%20are%20responsible.%20The%20problem%20of%20hate%20speech%20is%20not%20good%20and%20nobody%20can%20accept%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20also%20directed%20the%20petitioner%20to%20collate%20all%20the%20material%2C%20including%20video%2C%20and%20submit%20them%20to%20the%20nodal%20officers%20appointed%20in%20pursuance%20to%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20October%202022%20judgment%20on%20hate%20speeches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObserving%20that%20hate%20speeches%20vitiate%20the%20atmosphere%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20said%20that%20wherever%20required%2C%20adequate%20police%20force%20or%20paramilitary%20force%20would%20be%20deployed%20and%20the%20authorities%2C%20including%20the%20police%2C%20will%20use%20CCTV%20cameras%20installed%20or%20record%2Fmake%20video%20recordings%20in%20all%20sensitive%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20ET%2C%20Justice%20Khanna%20suggested%20that%20a%20DGP-led%20committee%20of%20three-four%20police%20officers%20%E2%80%93%20nominated%20by%20the%20DGP%20%E2%80%93%20examine%20complaints%20and%20the%20veracity%20of%20the%20allegations.%20If%20found%20true%2C%20the%20bench%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdirections%20can%20be%20issued%20to%20the%20police%20authorities%20to%20act%20against%20the%20miscreants%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20counsel%20for%20the%20Union%20government%20said%20the%20government%20does%20not%20support%20hate%20speech.%20The%20counsel%20added%20that%20in%20some%20places%20the%20mechanism%20to%20tackle%20hate%20speech%20was%20not%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691824553000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F22114407%2Fsupreme-court.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-hate-speech-unacceptable-centre-committee-haryana-violence%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20court%20made%20these%20observations%20during%20the%20resumed%20hearing%20of%20a%20plea%20seeking%20action%20against%20those%20who%20called%20for%20the%20social%20and%20economic%20boycott%20of%20the%20Muslim%20commu