ties%2C%20and%20the%20Pakistan%20Peoples%20Party%20(PPP)%2C%20also%20comes%20to%20an%20end.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20outgoing%20PM%20and%20the%20opposition%20leader%20in%20the%20NA%20have%2072%20hours%20to%20agree%20upon%20a%20nominee%20to%20lead%20the%20caretaker%20government%20to%20oversee%20the%20fresh%20general%20elections%2C%20which%20should%20be%20held%20within%2060%20days%20if%20the%20NA%20were%20dissolved%20after%20completing%20its%20full%20term.%20But%20in%20a%20tactical%20move%2C%20the%20outgoing%20coalition%20agreed%20to%20dissolve%20the%20NA%20three%20days%20before%20its%20end%20date%20of%20August%2012%2C%20thereby%20extending%20the%20deadline%20for%20the%20new%20polls%20by%20an%20additional%2030%20days.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20that%E2%80%99s%20not%20it.%20Just%20last%20week%2C%20the%20coalition%20government%20chose%20to%20certify%20new%20census%20results%2C%20which%20it%20had%20been%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-digital-census%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esitting%20on%20since%20May%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20This%20triggered%20a%20constitutional%20requirement%20to%20hold%20the%20next%20elections%20according%20to%20the%20new%20population%20data%2C%20which%20entails%20delimitation%20of%20constituencies%20that%20would%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fpakistans-general-elections-under-new-census-indicates-delay-2023-08-05%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edelay%20the%20polls%20by%20several%20months%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20new%20elections%2C%20therefore%2C%20are%20highly%20unlikely%20to%20be%20held%20this%20year.%20In%20fact%2C%20yet%20another%20move%20by%20the%20outgoing%20dispensation%20to%20give%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fexplainer-pakistan-has-just-given-more-powers-to-its-caretaker-government-and-it-is-not-good-news%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eextraordinary%20powers%20to%20the%20caretaker%20government%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20beyond%20their%20usual%20remit%20of%20conducting%20polls%2C%20has%20led%20to%20speculation%20about%20whether%20elections%20would%20be%20held%20at%20all%20in%20the%20foreseeable%20future.%20There%20already%20are%20caretaker%20governments%20in%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Khyber-Pakhtunkhwa%20(KP)%20provinces%20which%20have%20been%20functioning%20unconstitutionally%20for%20several%20months.%20The%20Senate%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20which%20is%20a%20permanent%20body%20elected%20indirectly%20through%20the%20provincial%20assemblies%2C%20has%20half%20its%20members%20retiring%20in%20March%202024.%20In%20principle%2C%20this%20sets%20a%20hard%20deadline%20at%20least%20for%20the%20provincial%20legislatures%20to%20be%20reelected%20by%20then.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20why%20does%20the%20PDM%20not%20want%20to%20face%20the%20electorate%3F%20Why%20go%20through%20such%20convoluted%20and%20controversial%20manoeuvres%3F%20The%20answer%20is%20the%20spectre%20of%20former%20PM%20Imran%20Khan%20returning%20to%20power.%20And%20in%20this%2C%20the%20PDM%20is%20joined%20by%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20all-powerful%20military%20and%2C%20especially%2C%20the%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%20(COAS)%20General%20Asim%20Munir%20%E2%80%93%20against%20whom%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20once%20the%20junta%E2%80%99s%20favourite%2C%20has%20a%20personal%20vendetta.%20After%20having%20been%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpakistan-elections-imran-khan%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Einstalled%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20into%20power%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fin-pakistan-the-junta-hangs-on-to-its-imran-khan-project%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esustained%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20then%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fin-dumping-imran-khan-pakistan-army-seeks-face-saving-not-course-correction%5C%22%