ehbaz%20Sharif%20government%20squandered%20the%20PML-N%E2%80%99s%20political%20capital.%20The%20junior%20coalition%20partners%2C%20like%20the%20PPP%20in%20its%20Sindh%20power%20base%2C%20remained%20somewhat%20insulated%20but%20not%20entirely%20unscathed.%20The%20PDM%20government%20appeared%20to%20be%20flailing%20helplessly%20and%2C%20terrified%20of%20elections%2C%20it%20held%20the%20army%20in%20an%20even%20tighter%20embrace.%20The%20brass%2C%20on%20its%20part%2C%20was%20concerned%20about%20Imran%20Khan%20seeking%20retribution%20against%20generals%2C%20especially%20the%20COAS%2C%20were%20he%20to%20return%20to%20power.%20To%20stop%20an%20ascendant%20Khan%2C%20the%20PDM-Army%20combine%20went%20into%20a%20hybrid-plus%20mode.%20The%20PDM%2C%20which%20had%20set%20out%20to%20undo%20the%20Imran-Bajwa%20hybrid%20regime%2C%20and%20the%20army%20that%20vowed%20to%20remain%20apolitical%2C%20converged%20into%20the%20hybrid%202.0%20dispensation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20he%20appeared%20formidable%2C%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20however%2C%20had%20made%20monumental%20blunders%20along%20the%20way.%20Strategic%20miscalculations%20and%20tactical%20missteps%20like%20dissolving%20his%20own%20governments%20in%20the%20Punjab%20and%20KP%20provinces%2C%20shunning%20the%20parliament%20in%20favour%20of%20street%20agitation%20which%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20muster%2C%20and%20spurning%20the%20PDM%20government%E2%80%99s%20overtures%20for%20rapprochement%20and%20fresh%20elections%2C%20were%20to%20haunt%20and%20frustrate%20him.%20He%20ratcheted%20up%20his%20rhetoric%20against%20the%20top%20brass%2C%20including%20the%20former%20and%20incumbent%20COAS%2C%20drawing%20a%20public%20rebuke%20from%20the%20ISPR.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20superior%20judiciary%20still%20protected%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20the%20army%20establishment%2C%20which%20had%20been%20mollycoddling%20him%20for%20years%2C%20stopped%20shielding%20him%20and%20possibly%20nudged%20the%20lower%20courts%20to%20proceed%20against%20him%20in%20a%20multitude%20of%20pending%20cases.%20The%20PDM%20government%20piled%20on%20with%20more%20charges%2C%20including%20murder%20and%20terrorism%2C%20sending%20the%20number%20of%20court%20cases%20against%20Imran%20Khan%20to%20almost%20as%20high%20as%20his%20ODI%20wickets%20tally.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20sheer%20desperation%2C%20Imran%20Khan%20went%20virtually%20rogue.%20Delusionally%20overconfident%20about%20his%20popular%20support%20and%20backed%20by%20elements%20within%20the%20armed%20forces%20and%20the%20judiciary%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20jostle%20his%20way%20back%20to%20power.%20When%20Khan%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1751782%2Fimran-khan-arrested-from-ihc-court-deems-ex-pms-arrest-legal%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eeventually%20arrested%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1751790%2Fimran-arrest-what-is-the-al-qadir-trust-case%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egraft%20charges%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20May%209%2C%20small%20protests%20erupted%20across%20the%20country%2C%20several%20of%20which%20went%20violent.%20Protestors%20breached%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nation.com.pk%2F10-May-2023%2Fghq-attacked-lahore-corps-commander-house-set-on-fire-by-pti-protesters%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGeneral%20Headquarters%20(GHQ)%20perimeter%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20Rawalpindi%2C%20set%20the%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-pti-imran-khan-protests-violence%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECorps%20Commander%20Lahore%E2%80%99s%20residence%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0and%20the%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.radio.gov.pk%2F15-05-2023%2Fburnt-building-of-radio-pakistan-peshawar-to-be-opened-for-public-today%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehistoric%20Radio%20Pakistan%20Peshawar%3C%2Fspan%3E%