he%20die%20was%20cast%3A%20only%20one%20of%20the%20two%20would%20remain%20standing.%20But%20the%20riot%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20trigger%20a%20rebellion%2C%20let%20alone%20the%20populist%20revolution%20that%20Imran%20Khan%20sought.%20The%20gamble%20had%20backfired.%20The%20army%20started%20a%20ruthless%20crackdown%20against%20the%20PTI%2C%20but%20the%20PDM%20government%20served%20as%20the%20face%20of%20it.%20Thousands%20of%20PTI%20workers%20and%20nearly%20all%20of%20its%20key%20leaders%20were%20arrested%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20will%20be%20tried%20in%20the%20military%20courts.%20The%20government%20ministers%20openly%20discussed%20the%20prospects%20of%20banning%20the%20PTI%20and%20trying%20Imran%20Khan%20himself%20under%20the%20draconian%20Army%20Act%20and%20the%20colonial-era%20Official%20Secrets%20Act.%20But%20the%20army%20instead%20opted%20to%20put%20its%20erstwhile%20darling%2C%20the%20PTI%2C%20on%20the%20chopping%20block.%20Clearly%20under%20duress%20from%20the%20junta%2C%20scores%20of%20PTI%20leaders%20have%20defected%2C%20denounced%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20publicly%20apologised%20for%20the%20May%209%20events%2C%20and%20pledged%20loyalty%20to%20the%20army.%20Most%20of%20these%20leaders%20were%20then%20herded%20into%20one%20new%20party%20and%20a%20new%20faction%20carved%20out%20of%20the%20PTI%2C%20while%20some%20have%20ostensibly%20quit%20politics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20then%20last%20week%2C%20a%20lower%20court%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Faug%2F05%2Fformer-pakistan-prime-minister-imran-khan-jailed-for-three-years%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econvicted%20and%20sentenced%20Imran%20Khan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20prison%20for%203%20years%20for%20misappropriation%20of%20state%20gifts%20and%20misdeclaration%20of%20assets.%20He%20was%20swiftly%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fpolice-arrest-former-pm-imran-khan-after-court-gives-three-year-prison-sentence-2023-08-05%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Earrested%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20incarcerated%20in%20the%20notoriously%20shabby%20Attock%20prison.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20of%20Pakistan%20(ECP)%20then%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F8%2F8%2Fformer-pakistan-pm-imran-khan-barred-from-politics-for-5-years%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edisqualified%20and%20barred%20him%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20politics%20for%205%20years%2C%20which%20could%20also%20result%20in%20him%20being%20prohibited%20from%20chairing%20his%20own%20party.%20Imran%20Khan%20has%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F09%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fimran-khan-appeal-prison-sentence.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eright%20of%20appeal(s)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20superior%20courts%2C%20but%20he%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20convicted%20and%20arrested%20in%20other%20cases%2C%20as%20the%20stage%20is%20being%20set%20to%20keep%20him%20from%20leading%20even%20his%20rump%20party%20in%20an%20election%2C%20if%20one%20is%20held%20at%20all.%20But%20the%20army%20most%20likely%20is%20not%20done%20with%20him%20and%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ecoup%20de%20gr%C3%A2ce%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20yet%20to%20come.%20What%20that%20might%20look%20like%20is%20hard%20to%20say%20as%20the%20junta%20seems%20to%20be%20weighing%20each%20option%20and%20the%20expected%20domestic%20and%20international%20response%20to%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F07221444%2FScreenshot-2023-06-07-at-10.13.10-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F07221444%2FScreenshot-2023-06-07-at-10.13.10-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F07221444%2FScreenshot-2023-06-07-at-10.13.10-PM-300x147.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F07221444%2FScreenshot-2023-06-07-at-10.13.10-PM-1024x500.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-657074%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22586%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPakistan%20Army%20chief%20General%20Asim%20Munir.%20Photo%3A%20Screengrab%20via%20YouTube%2FISPR%20Official%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20is%20clear%20though%20is%20that%20the%20political%20class%20in%20Pakistan%20has%20learnt%20no%20lesson.%20Six%20years%20ago%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fpakistan-politics-idINKCN1G51MI%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENawaz%20Sharif%20stood%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20where%20Imran%20Khan%20stands%20today%3A%20convicted%2C%20imprisoned%20and%20debarred%20from%20politics%20over%20fabricated%20charges%20by%20an%20army-judiciary%20combine%2C%20with%20which%20Imran%20Khan%20had%20made%20a%20common%20cause.%20Whether%20Imran%20Khan%20is%20actually%20guilty%20of%20wrongdoing%20has%20been%20rendered%20irrelevant%20by%20the%20PDM-army%20nexus%20dismembering%20his%20party%20through%20yet%20another%20dreadful%20exercise%20in%20political%20engineering.%20True%20that%20Imran%20Khan%20has%20only%20himself%20to%20blame%20for%20ditching%20parliament%20and%20dissing%20the%20dialogue%20with%20political%20opponents%2C%20but%20the%20PDM%20cannot%20be%20absolved%20of%20bending%20and%20flouting%20the%20law%20to%20ostensibly%20give%20him%20a%20taste%20of%20his%20own%20medicine.%20The%20PTI%20and%20the%20PDM%E2%80%99s%20stints%20were%20effectively%20a%20throwback%20to%20the%201990s%2C%20when%20the%20PML-N%20and%20the%20PPP%20took%20turns%20seeking%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20patronage%20to%20batter%2C%20bruise%20and%20bump%20each%20other%20out%20every%20two%20to%20three%20years.%20The%20only%20outcome%20of%20such%20hobnobbing%20%E2%80%93%20then%2C%20now%2C%20and%20ever%20%E2%80%93%20to%20subvert%20the%20constitution%20and%20undermine%20the%20parliament%2C%20is%20crippling%20an%20already%20measly%20democracy%20while%20strengthening%20the%20army%20behemoth.%20In%20this%2C%20the%20outgoing%20NA%20may%20rank%20perhaps%20the%20worst%20even%20by%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20atrocious%20democratic%20standards.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20the%20PTI%20ruled%20by%20proclaiming%20ordinances%20from%20the%20high%20horse%20of%20hybrid%20regime%2C%20the%20PDM%E2%80%99s%20hybrid%202.0%20plunged%20to%20new%20lows%20by%20passing%20laws%20and%20amending%20the%20existing%20ones%20through%20stealth%20and%20subterfuge%20at%20breakneck%20speed.%20And%20each%20piece%20of%20legislation%20steamrolled%20thus%20is%20more%20repugnant%20to%20the%20spirit%20of%20democracy%20and%20the%20letter%20of%20the%20constitution%20than%20the%20other.%20And%20it%20was%20all%20done%20merely%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftribune.com.pk%2Fstory%2F2428508%2Fgovt-rushes-crucial-bills-as-term-nears-end%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edays%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20hours%20before%20the%20NA%20ended%20its%20term%2C%20as%20if%20someone%20was%20holding%20a%20gun%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20head.%20After%20the%20PTI%E2%80%99s%20departure%20from%20the%20NA%2C%20there%20is%20no%20legitimate%20opposition%20left%20in%20the%20house.%20The%20ostensible%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20is%20a%20PTI%20defector%20who%20is%20reportedly%20going%20to%20contest%20the%20elections%20on%20a%20PML-N%20ticket.%20But%20despite%20that%2C%20in%20unholy%20haste%2C%20the%20government%20didn%E2%80%99t%20share%20some%20proposed%20Bills%20even%20with%20the%20treasury%20benches%2C%20forcing%20members%20to%20protest.%20A%20PML-N%20loyalist%20and%20former%20PM%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftribune.com.pk%2Fstory%2F2430026%2Fabbasi-terms-current-na-worst-in-pakistans-history%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EShahid%20Khaqan%20Abbasi%20apologised%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20the%20people%20for%20this%20%E2%80%98shameful%E2%80%99%20NA.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20amendments%20rammed%20through%20the%20parliament%20included%20changes%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1767984%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOfficial%20Secrets%20Act%2C%201923%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftribune.com.pk%2Fstory%2F2428164%2Fbill-ratifies-army-role-in-national-development%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EArmy%20Act%2C%201952%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20former%20law%20now%20gives%20sweeping%20powers%20to%20the%20military%20intelligence%20agencies%2C%20including%20the%20ISI%2C%20to%20raid%20any%20premises%20and%20detain%20any%20citizen%2C%20even%20under%20the%20mere%20suspicion%20of%20them%20breaching%20the%20law%2C%20and%20authorises%20them%20to%20use%20force%20if%20resisted.%20All%20they%20need%20is%20a%20nominal%20warrant.%20In%20an%20eerily%20Orwellian%20manner%2C%20the%20law%20also%20empowers%20these%20agencies%20with%20dystopian%20definitions%20of%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98document%E2%80%99%20to%20include%20unwritten%20and%20intangible%20materials%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98enemy%E2%80%99%20to%20include%20even%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eunintentionally%20interacting%20with%20a%20person%20or%20entity%20that%20these%20outfits%20might%20consider%20hostile%20to%20the%20country.%20While%20some%20of%20the%20changes%20may%20be%20directed%20at%20the%20military%20personnel%20who%20are%20already%20being%20acted%20against%20for%20acts%20of%20omission%20or%20commission%20on%20May%209%2C%20the%20thrust%20of%20the%20amendment%20is%20to%20give%20legal%20cover%20to%20the%20ISI%E2%80%99s%20dirty%20tactics%20against%20dissidents%20of%20all%20shades.%20In%20effect%2C%20it%20provides%20%E2%80%93%20under%20the%20veneer%20of%20a%20nominal%20search%20warrant%20%E2%80%93%20the%20military%20intelligence%20agencies%20with%20the%20same%20powers%20that%20were%20once%20exercised%20by%20the%20Nazi%20Schutzstaffel%20(SS).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20amendments%20to%20the%20Army%20Act%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20formalise%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20not%20just%20domestic%20commercial%20and%20investment%20enterprises%20but%20also%20sovereign%20state-to-state%20ventures.%20The%20insertion%20reads%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPakistan%20Army%20may%2C%20upon%20direction%20or%20with%20the%20concurrence%20of%20relevant%20authorities%20of%20the%20appropriate%20government%20in%20the%20prescribed%20manner%2C%20directly%20or%20indirectly%2C%20carry%20out%20activities%20related%20to%2C%20inter%20alia%2C%20national%20development%20and%20advancement%20of%20national%20or%20strategic%20interest%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ostensible%20national%20development%2C%20the%20national%20or%20strategic%20interest%2C%20and%20its%20advancement%2C%20however%2C%20have%20not%20been%20defined.%20The%20amendment%20also%20gives%20a%20retrospective%20legal%20cover%20to%20the%20military%E2%80%99s%20commercial%20activities%20in%20the%20past.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20parliament%20also%20hastily%20approved%20the%20Board%20of%20Investment%20(Amendment)%20Act%2C%202023%2C%20authorising%20the%20Special%20Investment%20Facilitation%20Council%20(SIFC)%2C%20which%20was%20formed%20through%20an%20ordinance%20as%20the%20PDM%20government%20ran%20up%20the%20exit%20ramp.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20and%20his%20ministers%20described%20it%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwhole%20government%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cone%20window%E2%80%9D%20operation%20to%20attract%20foreign%20investment%2C%20especially%20from%20the%20Gulf%20countries%2C%20it%20effectively%20is%20a%20hybrid%20civil-military%20body%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.arabnews.pk%2Fnode%2F2325301%2Fpakistan%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eformalising%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20yet%20another%20economic%20entity%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20army%20chief%20will%20sit%20in%20the%20SFIC%20apex%20committee%2C%20along%20with%20the%20PM%2C%20while%20army%20officials%20will%20head%20its%20national%20coordination%2C%20implementation%20and%20executive%20levels.%20The%20hybrid%202.0%20regime%20is%20calling%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenews.com.pk%2Fprint%2F1094271-sifc-a-consequence-of-exceptional-trust-level-between-pm-army-chief%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESFIC%20a%20game%20changer%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ewith%20a%20scale%20larger%20than%20the%20China-Pakistan%20Economic%20Corridor%20(CPEC).%20Whether%20the%20project%20attracts%20investments%20such%20as%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fgulf-nations-poised-to-invest-billions-in-pakistan-as-it-seeks-infusion-of-foreign-currency-9dfbb2ad%3Fst%3Ds1ecge60y4kzjwd%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESaudis%20potentially%20buying%20out%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20shares%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20a%20copper%20mine%20in%20Balochistan%20or%20stagnates%20like%20the%20CPEC%2C%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1769036%2Fcpec-to-sifc%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eup%20for%20debate%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20preeminence%20in%20the%20project%20indicates%20more%20than%20just%20reassuring%20the%20jittery%20Arab%20investors%20of%20ease%20of%20doing%20business.%20It%20indicates%20that%20the%20governance%20paradigm%20has%20undergone%20a%20tectonic%20shift%20over%20the%20term%20of%20the%20outgoing%20NA.%20Failure%20of%20the%20first%20hybrid%20regime%2C%20Imran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20botched%20putsch%2C%20and%20the%20meek%20and%20mediocre%20PDM-PPP%20regime%20have%20all%20collectively%20enabled%20the%20army%20under%20General%20Munir%20to%20make%20a%20power%20and%20governance%20grab%20not%20seen%20since%201958%20when%20General%20Ayub%20Khan%20imposed%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20first%20martial%20law.%20Pakistan%2C%20since%20then%2C%20has%20been%20a%20coup-prone%20state%2C%20which%20oscillates%20between%20direct%20army%20rule%20or%20an%20indirect%20one%20where%20the%20junta%20rules%20through%20controlled%20democracies.%20Eric%20Nordlinger%20noted%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%2Fabout%2FSoldiers_in_Politics.html%3Fid%3D1tAWAAAAIAAJ%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESoldiers%20in%20Politics%3A%20Military%20Coups%20and%20Governments%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20most%20frequent%20sequel%20to%20military%20coups%20and%20government%20is%20more%20of%20the%20same%E2%80%A6%20The%20aftermath%20of%20military%20intervention%20is%20military%20intervention.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20PDM-PPP%20regime%20exits%20the%20stage%2C%20it%20is%20not%20a%20question%20of%20whether%20Pakistan%20would%20remain%20under%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20boot%20or%20not%2C%20but%20of%20what%20form%20that%20might%20be%20in.%20The%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20government%E2%80%99s%20abject%20abdication%20of%20the%20political%20and%20governance%20space%20to%20the%20army%20and%20enabling%20the%20junta%20constitutionally%20and%20legally%20to%20sit%20atop%20the%20economic%20commanding%20heights%20has%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20an%20Indonesian-style%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F24490795%3Fread-now%3D1%26seq%3D4%23page_scan_tab_contents%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDwifungsi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20%E2%80%9Cdual%20function%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Dwifungsi%20expanded%20the%20role%20of%20armed%20forces%20from%20territorial%20defence%20to%20involvement%20in%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20political%2C%20economic%20and%20social%20order.%20Under%20the%20dictator%20Suharto%2C%20army%20officers%20not%20only%20held%20positions%20in%20government%20ministries%20and%20corporations%20but%20were%20also%20given%2020%25%20seats%20in%20the%20parliament.%20The%202018-2023%20hybrid%20experiment%20in%20Pakistan%20has%20afforded%20all%20but%20the%20nominal%20perch%20in%20the%20parliament%20to%20serving%20officers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20did%20not%20have%20to%20turn%20out%20this%20way%2C%20and%20certainly%20did%20not%20end%20in%20such%20ignominy%20for%20the%20PDM%20politicians.%20But%20this%20was%20a%20choice%20they%20made%20when%20signing%20the%20Faustian%20bargain%20with%20the%20army.%20They%20opted%20for%20political%20expediency%20over%20struggle%2C%20and%20hand-me-down%20diluted%20power%20over%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20mandate.%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eet%20al%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20chose%20a%20military%20solution%20to%20a%20civilian%20problem%2C%20which%20inevitably%20brings%20the%20army%20out%20of%20the%20garrisons%20not%20push%20it%20back%20into%20the%20barracks.%20Khan%20indeed%20is%20a%20problem%20of%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20making%20but%20relying%20on%20the%20army%20to%20dismantle%20him%20ensured%20the%20junta%E2%80%99s%20continued%20involvement%20in%20political%20engineering%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20preeminence.%20Chasing%20the%20mirage%20of%20power%20instead%20of%20going%20for%20fresh%20elections%20a%20year-and-a-half%20ago%2C%20when%20Nawaz%20Sharif%E2%80%99s%20slogan%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EVote%20ko%20izzat%20do%3C%2Fem%3E%20(respect%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20vote)%E2%80%99%20carried%20weight%20and%20Imran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20chips%20were%20down%2C%20had%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20the%20disgraceful%20flight%20from%20polls%20today.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20buck%2C%20however%2C%20stops%20with%20Mian%20Nawaz%20Sharif%2C%20as%20the%20PDM%20effectively%20ruled%20in%20his%20name.%20While%20he%20may%20be%20away%20and%20constrained%20by%20legal%2C%20family%20and%20clique%20issues%20%E2%80%93%20but%20ultimately%20it%20is%20his%20party%2C%20his%20vote%20bank%2C%20and%20above%20all%20his%20stance%20that%20took%20the%20ultimate%20hit.%20Imran%20Khan%20may%20have%20been%20knocked%20out%20but%20was%20it%20worth%20the%20price%20paid%20in%20political%20capital%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F27162247%2Fnawaz-sharif-pti_0_0_0_0.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22701%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F27162247%2Fnawaz-sharif-pti_0_0_0_0.jpg%20620w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F27162247%2Fnawaz-sharif-pti_0_0_0_0-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-283531%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22467%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFormer%20prime%20minister%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20Nawaz%20Sharif.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20way%20the%2015%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20NA%20divested%20itself%20of%20its%20own%20powers%20and%20surrendered%20its%20constitutional%20domain%20to%20the%20army%20is%20surpassed%20only%20by%20the%201985%20party-less%207%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20NA%20under%20General%20Ziaul%20Haq.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20even%20that%20assembly%20took%20almost%20six%20months%20to%20pass%20the%20infamous%208%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Amendment%20giving%20the%20vile%20and%20wily%20dictator%20unbridled%20power%20to%20dissolve%20the%20assemblies.%20That%20virulent%20mutation%2C%20however%2C%20could%20not%20be%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.loc.gov%2Fitem%2Fglobal-legal-monitor%2F2010-06-15%2Fpakistan-amendment-to-constitution-reduces-presidential-power%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eremedied%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20another%2025%20years.%20The%20outgoing%20PDM%20government%20may%20have%20prevailed%20against%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20but%20the%20way%20Pakistan%20has%20regressed%20to%20a%20fully-blown%20praetorian%20state%2C%20it%20sure%20looks%20like%20a%20Pyrrhic%20victory.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fmohammad-taqi%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMohammad%20Taqi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20Pakistani-American%20columnist.%20He%20tweets%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmazdaki%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%40mazdaki%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691821930000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F12115832%2Fshehbaz-sharif.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-full-blown-praetorian-state-shehbaz-sharif-imran-khan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20government%E2%80%99s%20abject%20abdication%20of%20the%20political%20and%20governance%20space%20to%20the%20army%20has%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20an%20Indonesian-style%20Dwifungsi%20or%20%E2%80%9Cdual%20function%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-full-blown-praetorian-state-shehbaz-sharif-imran-khan%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22KJo%2C%20Kartik%20to%20collaborate%20for%20a%20film%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691821114000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102670752%2Cimgsize-39628.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatim