acefully.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20long-standing%20position%20on%20the%20need%20to%20adhere%20to%20the%20international%20law%20in%20the%20context%20of%20issues%20relating%20to%20South%20China%20Sea%20and%20also%20for%20a%20rules%20based%20order%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBagchi%20underlined%20that%20India%20had%20always%20the%20need%20for%20peaceful%20settlements%20of%20disputes.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20certainly%20urge%20the%20parties%20to%20follow%20that%20as%20well%20as%20ensure%20that%20these%20incidents%20do%20not%20happen%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20an%20international%20arbitral%20tribunal%2C%20established%20under%20United%20Nations%20Convention%20on%20the%20Law%20of%20the%20Sea%20(UNCLOS)%2C%20invalidating%20China%E2%80%99s%20claims%20in%202016%2C%20China%20persists%20in%20asserting%20ownership%20over%20nearly%20the%20entire%20South%20China%20Sea%20and%20dismissing%20the%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Ffor-the-first-time-india-calls-for-abiding-by-the-2016-arbitral-award-on-south-china-sea%5C%22%3EIndia%20has%20recently%20changed%20its%20position%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20asked%20for%20parties%20to%20abide%20by%20the%202016%20arbitration%20award.%20The%20change%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20posture%20was%20mentioned%20in%20a%20joint%20statement%20issued%20by%20India%20and%20the%20Philippines%20after%20the%20fifth%20Joint%20Commission%20on%20bilateral%20cooperation%20during%20the%20visit%20of%20the%20Filipino%20foreign%20minister%20to%20New%20Delhi%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20(the%20ministers)%20underlined%20the%20need%20for%20a%20peaceful%20settlement%20of%20disputes%20and%20for%20an%20adherence%20to%20international%20law%2C%20especially%20the%20UNCLOS%20and%20the%202016%20Arbitral%20Award%20on%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20in%20this%20regard%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20joint%20statement%20dated%20June%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MEA%20spokesperson%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20reiterate%20the%20reference%20to%20the%20adherence%20to%20the%202016%20ruling%20in%20his%20statement%20at%20the%20media%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691769600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F640x640-2-6.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Famid-tensions-over-south-china-sea-india-tells-china-philippines-to-adhere-to-global-law%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Last%20weekend%20the%20Philippines%20accused%20the%20Chinese%20coast%20guard%20of%20firing%20water%20cannons%20to%20stop%20movement%20of%20its%20vessels%20in%20South%20China%20Sea.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Famid-tensions-over-south-china-sea-india-tells-china-philippines-to-adhere-to-global-law%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine%20fires%20military%20conscription%20officials%20for%20taking%20bribes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691768582000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F37BB%2Fproduction%2F_130776241_a8da373973db3ed9d383a0d154c9c08d3bce7a4f0_0_2759_19301000x700.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66478422%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Officials%20took%20cash%20and%20cryptocurrency%20and%20helped%20people%20to%20leave%20Ukraine%2C%20President%20Zelensky%20says.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2204%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66478422%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66478422.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66478422.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Musk%20says%20cage%20fight%20with%20Zuckerberg%20will%20be%20in%20Italy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publ