ess-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findustrial-production-rises-3-7-in-june-against-5-3-in-may-nso-data-123081100618_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findustrial-production-rises-3-7-in-june-against-5-3-in-may-nso-data-123081100618_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Heritage%20Building%20in%20Hyderabad%20Has%20Seen%20the%20World%E2%80%99s%20Most%20Significant%20Medical%20Breakthroughs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2027%2C%20the%20Telangana%20government%20submitted%20an%20affidavit%20before%20the%20Telangana%20High%20Court%20announcing%20its%20decision%20to%20demolish%20all%20buildings%20that%20form%20part%20of%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F98540%2Fcelebrating-100-years-osmania-university-alumni-adopt-villages%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Osmania%20General%20Hospital%20(OGH)%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecampus%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20heritage%20block.%20In%20its%20place%2C%20the%20government%20plans%20to%20build%20a%20new%201800-bed%20facility.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20currently%20several%20public%20interest%20litigations%20(PIL)%20in%20the%20High%20Court%20that%20seek%20to%20preserve%20the%20heritage%20block.%C2%A0%20For%20instance%2C%20one%20filed%20by%20social%20activist%20Lubna%20Sarwath%20calls%20the%20demolition%20unconstitutional%20which%20will%20%E2%80%9Churt%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20identity%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20State%20cannot%20afford%20the%20luxury%20of%20forgetting%20that%20the%20destruction%20of%20heritage%20buildings%20will%20rob%20its%20people%20of%20the%20essence%20of%20their%20identity%2C%20and%20will%20deprive%20the%20city%20of%20its%20sense%20of%20uniqueness.%20While%20it%20is%20important%20to%20plan%20for%20the%20future%2C%20it%20is%20equally%20important%20to%20protect%2C%20to%20preserve%20and%20to%20promote%20the%20past%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sarw