3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20at%20these%20two%20buildings%20that%20major%20medical%20breakthroughs%20were%20made.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20discovery%20of%20malaria%20was%20made%20at%20the%20Hyderabad%20Medical%20School%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F272865%2Fhyderabad-fever-hospital-sir-ronald-ross-nobel-prize-malaria%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENobel%20laureate%20Sir%20Ronald%20Ross%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Afzal%20Gunj%20Hospital%20contributed%20to%20a%20major%20breakthrough%20in%20anesthesia.%20The%20first%20international%20chloroform%20trials%2C%20backed%20by%20the%20sixth%20Nizam%20Mir%20Mahboob%20Ali%20Khan%2C%20took%20place%20in%20this%20hospital%20from%201888%20to%201891%2C%20and%20were%20conducted%20by%20his%20personal%20physician%20Dr%20Edward%20Lawrie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chloroform%20Commission%20conducted%20experiments%20to%20establish%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20chloroform%20as%20an%20anesthetic%20to%20treat%20patients.%20It%20was%20a%20major%20breakthrough%20that%20led%20to%20several%20lives%20being%20saved%20in%20the%20future.%20While%20the%20chemical%20was%20being%20used%20for%20surgical%20procedures%2C%20this%20trial%20helped%20in%20determining%20how%20it%20could%20be%20used%20safely.%20The%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20report%20would%20go%20on%20to%20be%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Lancet%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilt%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20floods%20and%20a%20plague%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2023-08-11T143636.627-1691745341.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20tamarind%20tree%20that%20saved%20the%20lives%20of%20150%20people%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%2